data.description: Cozy yet huge! This spacious home sits on over half an acre with a huge backyard and a scattering of matured trees and encompassing it all is a driveway that circles the home. Inside, the many skylights and windows fill the home with an abundance of sunlight. They shine your path through the den and dining rooms and lead you into the open, updated kitchen with warm and rustic finishes like the butcherblock eat-in peninsula and travertine backsplash. Quartz countertops, a gas stove top and a built-in breakfast nook complete the beautiful kitchen. The living room features a spectacular retro-style fireplace with attached stairs leading to the magnificently large Gameroom. Upstairs offers the perfect oasis allowing for privacy and convenience with a large bedroom, bathroom and study. See it for yourself! Schedule a tour today and Own Your Paradise!
